### Spacing System

The spacing system uses a fluid calculation based on viewport width with a multiplier system:

```css
:root {
  --dw: 1920;                    /* Design width (desktop) */
  --multiplier: 0.3;             /* Spacing multiplier */
  --spacing: clamp(
    1 * (1 - var(--multiplier)) / 16 * 1rem,
    1 / var(--dw) * 100vw,
    1 * (1 + var(--multiplier)) / 16 * 1rem
  );
  --container-spacing: calc(var(--spacing) * 50);
}

/* Tablet adjustments */
@media screen and (max-width: 1023px) {
  :root {
